00:15:50,460 --> 00:15:51,250
Karin-chan.

232
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:52,210
Áno?

233
00:15:52,420 --> 00:15:53,880
Už je neskoro.

234
00:15:54,540 --> 00:15:56,090
Môžeš ísť.

235
00:15:56,630 --> 00:15:57,090
Okay.

236
00:15:57,670 --> 00:16:00,220
Usui-kun ťa aj dnes odprevadí domov.

237
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:02,800
Už som sa ho na to spýtal.

238
00:16:02,970 --> 00:16:03,470
Okay.

239
00:16:10,100 --> 00:16:11,980
<I>Vedúci, ani neviete čo ste spôsobili...</I>

240
00:16:12,690 --> 00:16:13,940
<I>Z tohto môžu byť problémy.</I>

241
00:16:14,350 --> 00:16:18,650
<I>Nemôžem sa k Usui-ovi priblížiť, kým nevymyslím nejaké protiopatrenie.</I>

242
00:16:22,150 --> 00:16:25,240
<I>Ale ja som sa rozhodla urobiť ho šťastným!</I>

243
00:16:26,030 --> 00:16:29,660
<I>Najdôležitejšie je dozvedieť sa čo najviac o subjekte! Čo najviac!</I>

244
00:16:31,620 --> 00:16:35,170
<I>Ale ak sa mi krv znovu vzbúri a začnem krvácať, neprežijem to!</I>

245
00:16:42,130 --> 00:16:43,510
Prepáč, že si musel čakať.

246
00:16:44,470 --> 00:16:44,930
V poriadku.

247
00:16:56,190 --> 00:17:00,320
<I>No tak, spýtaj sa ho, Karin! Spýtaj sa, kedy je Usui-kun najšťastnejší!</I>

248
00:17:02,190 --> 00:17:02,900
Um...
Um...

249
00:17:05,660 --> 00:17:07,280
Usui-kun, ty prvý.

250
00:17:07,780 --> 00:17:08,280
Oh.

251
00:17:09,280 --> 00:17:10,540
Um, er...

252
00:17:11,870 --> 00:17:14,830
To je v poriadku, Tokitou mi dala svoju desiatu.

253
00:17:16,710 --> 00:17:22,010
Zabudol som jej to vrátiť, tak sa chcem
spýtať, či jej to nedáš.

254
00:17:23,590 --> 00:17:24,300
Môžeš?

255
00:17:29,470 --> 00:17:29,930
Um...

256
00:17:30,970 --> 00:17:31,600
To...

257
00:17:32,810 --> 00:17:34,270
...bola moja desiata.

258
00:17:36,520 --> 00:17:37,350
Oh, tvoja?

259
00:17:38,980 --> 00:17:42,860
Bolo to výborné. Maaka, tvoja mama varí dobre.

260
00:17:43,490 --> 00:17:44,110
Um...

261
00:17:45,110 --> 00:17:46,530
Ja som to robila.

262
00:17:47,450 --> 00:17:47,990
Vážne.

263
00:17:49,120 --> 00:17:49,910
Bolo to vynikajúce.

264
00:17:52,950 --> 00:17:55,830
Musím ešte nakúpiť, zvládneš to odtiaľto?

265
00:17:57,540 --> 00:17:58,330
Okay...

266
00:17:59,000 --> 00:17:59,540
Zatiaľ.

267
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:05,840
Tadaima.

268
00:18:07,130 --> 00:18:10,220
Onee-chan, už si zistila čo je šťastie?

269
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:14,430
Ešte nie. Ale stále na tom pracujem!

270
00:18:14,680 --> 00:18:15,140
Určite.

271
00:18:16,230 --> 00:18:16,940
Oh.

272
00:18:17,140 --> 00:18:19,150
Ja som to hneď pochopil.

273
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:20,060
Áno, to určite.

274
00:18:20,860 --> 00:18:25,990
Je to niečo čomu ty nechápeš, takže ti to vysvetlím...

275
00:18:26,570 --> 00:18:28,660
Takže? Moje šťastie je...

276
00:18:28,660 --> 00:18:30,070
Úplne čisté.

277
00:18:30,820 --> 00:18:32,200
Usui-kun je úžasný.

278
00:18:32,620 --> 00:18:34,740
Aj keď je to chlapec, umyl to dobre.

279
00:18:37,370 --> 00:18:38,250
Bolo to vynikajúce.

280
00:18:41,250 --> 00:18:42,960
On vyzeral šťastný.

281
00:18:44,380 --> 00:18:45,960
Ak sa nad tým zamyslím...

282
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:49,010
..krv sa mi nevzbúrila...

283
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:53,510
Keď Usui-kun zjedol moje jedlo, nešťastie zmizlo?

284
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:56,640
Jedlo?!

285
00:18:56,850 --> 00:18:59,520
...a pretože je to tak, šťastie je...

286
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:00,520
Pochopila som

287
00:19:02,270 --> 00:19:02,980
Vážne?

288
00:19:03,060 --> 00:19:06,190
Presne! Jedlo je šťastie!

289
00:19:08,360 --> 00:19:12,160
Výborne! Takže mu každý deň jedno urobím!

290
00:19:15,540 --> 00:19:16,370
Haló?

291
00:19:17,080 --> 00:19:19,500
Maki? Práve som ti chcela zavolať!

292
00:19:20,710 --> 00:19:23,920
Máš doma nejaké recepty?

293
00:19:24,380 --> 00:19:25,960
Daj mi nejaké, no tak, no tak?

294
00:19:27,420 --> 00:19:28,050
Dobre.

295
00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:30,340
Zajtra ti ich prinesiem.

296
00:19:31,130 --> 00:19:31,760
Prosím!

297
00:19:33,220 --> 00:19:33,720
Áno.

298
00:19:35,220 --> 00:19:35,810
Rozumiem.

299
00:19:37,390 --> 00:19:38,770
Takže, uvidíme sa zajtra.

300
00:19:40,230 --> 00:19:40,980
Ojasumi.
(Dobrú noc)

301
00:19:42,810 --> 00:19:45,730
Dobre! Teraz si budem môcť vybrať zo širokej ponuky jedál!

302
00:19:46,070 --> 00:19:46,360
Huh?

303
00:19:47,570 --> 00:19:50,280
Ale čo má vlastne Usui-kun rád.

304
00:19:51,320 --> 00:19:53,450
Mala som sa spýtať!

305
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:55,580
Som taký blbec, blbec, blbec!

306
00:19:59,450 --> 00:20:00,790
Tadaima!

307
00:20:01,670 --> 00:20:02,830
Vitaj, Mama.

308
00:20:03,460 --> 00:20:06,710
Idem neskoro, lebo som mala množstvo pohovorov.

309
00:20:07,460 --> 00:20:08,590
Prepáč mi to.

310
00:20:09,550 --> 00:20:10,260
Ako to šlo?

311
00:20:10,970 --> 00:20:12,880
Zle, všetky zle.

312
00:20:15,050 --> 00:20:15,510
Oh.

313
00:20:15,680 --> 00:20:19,310
Oh nie! Kenta, nemusíš sa trápiť!

314
00:20:20,560 --> 00:20:22,690
Pokaziť jeden alebo dva pohovory...

315
00:20:23,100 --> 00:20:24,400
...alebo tri či štyri...

316
00:20:24,600 --> 00:20:27,860
...prípadne päť alebo šesť je normálne.

317
00:20:28,020 --> 00:20:30,570
Som si istá, že som sa aj tak na tú prácu nehodila.

318
00:20:31,110 --> 00:20:35,120
To je v poriadku! Zajtra si už nájdem skvelú prácu!

319
00:20:37,780 --> 00:20:39,240
Ak si šťastná, mama.

320
00:20:39,450 --> 00:20:42,540
Huh? Ale ja som stále šťastná.

321
00:20:47,090 --> 00:20:48,090
Mám ťa!

322
00:20:48,750 --> 00:20:50,340
Čo si taký prekvapený?

323
00:20:57,550 --> 00:20:58,180
Nemožné...

324
00:20:58,470 --> 00:20:58,850
Huh?

325
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:02,310
To sú kúsance od Maaky.
(Sorry za výraz)

326
00:21:03,060 --> 00:21:04,600
Maaka je upír?

327
00:21:06,690 --> 00:21:07,400
Nemožné.

328
00:21:07,770 --> 00:21:08,360
Nie?

329
00:21:09,270 --> 00:21:11,650
Tak, čo urobím?

330
00:21:12,610 --> 00:21:15,410
To vyzerá dobre. Oh, to tiež!

331
00:21:40,720 --> 00:21:47,270
Kimi ni au toki ga ichiban ureshii
It's when I see you that I'm the happiest.

332
00:21:48,310 --> 00:21:54,570
Kimi ni au toki ga ichiban kurushii kedo
It's when I see you that it hurts the most, but...

333
00:21:56,110 --> 00:22:02,950
Afuredasu omoi wo moshi uchiagete shimattara, ne
I wonder what kind of future would come...

334
00:22:03,450 --> 00:22:08,500
Donna mirai ga kuru ka na
...If I let this overflowing feeling out.

335
00:22:09,500 --> 00:22:13,050
Suki na hito ni suki to ieru
Being able to tell the person you love that you love him...

336
00:22:13,300 --> 00:22:16,760
Kirameku tokubetsu na yume
...would be a special sparkling dream...

337
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:20,600
Kizu tsuku koto mo nanimo osorezu
...If you can start runnning without being afraid...

338
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:24,470
kakedashite yukeru no nara
...of getting hurt or anything else.

339
00:22:24,640 --> 00:22:28,230
Suki na hito ni suki to ieru
If I can tell the person I love that I love him...

340
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:31,940
Sono hi wa atarashii BIRTHDAY
...then that day would become my new birthday...

341
00:22:32,270 --> 00:22:36,070
Kinou to chigau watashi ni natte
...and I'll become a me different from yesterday...

342
00:22:36,110 --> 00:22:44,790
mayowazu ni tokihanasu yo MY LOVE FOR YOU
...and set free my love for you without it getting lost.

343
00:22:55,550 --> 00:22:57,970
Môžem ti to povedať, Onii-chan?

344
00:22:59,010 --> 00:23:01,510
aká je sestrina pravá podoba...

345
00:23:02,600 --> 00:23:06,350
Nabudúce v Karin: Byť odhalená je ponižujúce.

346
00:23:07,850 --> 00:23:09,350
Ona už znovu zaspala.

